<section xml:id="policies" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Course Policies and Procedures</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>
      At a minimum, all policies stated in the current <url href="https://www.latech.edu/documents/2018/09/student-handbook.pdf/" visual="">Louisiana Tech University Student Handbook</url> should be followed.
      Additional class policies follow.
    </p>
  </introduction>
  
  <subsection xml:id="textbook">
    <title>Textbook</title>
