      <title>Required Textbook</title>
      <p component="ULA">
	The required text for this course is
	<pubtitle>Understanding Linear Algebra</pubtitle> by David Austin.
	This textbook is freely available in 
	<url href="https://understandinglinearalgebra.org/ula.html" visual="understandinglinearalgebra.org/ula.html"><init>HTML</init> format</url>
